commit.title: Test relevance before structural equality for rels and constants
commit.message:
Test relevance before structural equality for rels and constants

This makes it possible to use SProp to avoid hard conversion problems,
instead of having to wait arbitrary amounts of time for them to fail.

See some discussion in https://github.com/coq/coq/pull/12041
